NA:
Audio / video recordings for the target of language revitalization and research on etymology: choose consultant with better language skills (probably elders); 
Audio / video recordings for the target of documenting the status quo, loan words etc.: choose consultants from all age groups and genders to compare differences; 
Transcription assistant: choose younger person with teeth (!)
Writing dictionaries / shool books: choose younger people with IT skills who cooperate with others (elders) who have the better language skills
Documenting taboo words, curses, lexicon of sexual organs: Choose consultants of your own gender
Create local teams to cooperate on one research topic: Might work with mixed age groups, but not in all communities. Experience from Khinalug: Choose consultants from one age group, who may ask informations from elders, but don't let elders join the team (otherwise the elders will dominate everything and annoy the other team members)
